Description:
Immaculately Presented - Excellent Location
This beautiful family home is an entertainers delight and is situated in one of Cobrams most popular, river end locations.
Features a spacious lounge, plus a large open plan kitchen/meals/living area with walk in pantry and sliding door access to the rear balcony/alfresco area. Four generous bedrooms plus study. Large main bedroom with ensuite. Ducted vacuum system, ducted gas heating, ducted evaporative cooling, and a double garage. Outside is an entertainers delight with an in-ground pool, balcony with alfresco area, outdoor kitchen with a barbecue and pizza oven, and of course, the "Man Cave" - 6m x 3m colorbond shed with a roller door. Side gate vehicle access to the rear yard and shed, perfect for boat or caravan storage.
Move in and enjoy, all the work is done.

Description:
Charming Three Bedroom Home
Lovely cottage style weatherboard home situated on the corner of Churr St and Wirbill St on a large sized block of approximately 960sqm . You will be pleasantly surprised when you step inside. This home has a centrally located kitchen with electric oven, gas cook top, dishwasher and plenty of cupboards. Polished timber floor boards throughout kitchen, meals, hallway and master bedroom. The three bedrooms are all a good size with ceiling fans to two bedrooms and built in robes to all bedrooms. The spacious light filled lounge has a gas log fireplace with the home also offering evaporative ducted cooling. Bathroom features shower over bath and vanity with laundry offering a separate shower. Externally there is a carport, garden shed and 6m x 5m (approx.) lock up shed with concrete floor and power with easy access for a boat or a caravan. First home buyers don't miss out, book an inspection today!

Description:
Absolutely Fabulous
Set in Green Palms Retirement Village Cobram, this stunning three bedroom home is only two years old and has it all. High ceilings, dual living areas, timber floors, outdoor deck facing the morning sun, and a large undercover outdoor entertaining area. This home is beautifully finished - the Helena Plus version - with many extras than the standard build, making it a stand out choice in the village.
Spacious open kitchen/meals/living, separate lounge, and three bedrooms - the main with walk-in robe & ensuite. Additional features include dual split system air conditioning, indoor shutters, bamboo floors, a larger than normal deck, landscaped surrounds, watering system, full fencing with front and rear gates, solar electricity system, roof vents on the patio and more.
A real pleasure, inspect soon as it won't last long.
